      "id": "PopularPost52773",
      "post_content": "Hybrid laces seem to me to be a good idea. They would cost 1 hybrid mana, and make the targeted permanant both the lace's colors. Granted, you wouldn't be able to use them to change the color of spells, but that's the trade-off for making stuff two colors, one of which isn't the color you paid for the spell. The change would still be permanant.",
