      "id": "PopularPost92028",
      "post_content": "Multicolored Laces would make them strictly worse. The only use I see for the laces is for getting around protection, multicolored one removes their one realistic use. Which makes them even less playable than they already on. Maybe a multicolored lace that lets you choose which colors you which of the two colors. Prismatic Lace is really the only one that playable and just barely.",
      "posted_by": "Deathtamoor",
      "html": "<div class=\"post evenItem\" id=\"PopularPost92028\" style=\"background-color: rgba(255,255,255,0.08);\">\n<span class=\"postContent\" id=\"ctl00_ctl00_ctl00_MainContent_SubContent_SubContent_popularPosts_postsRepeater_ctl02_post\">Multicolored Laces would make them strictly worse.  The only use I see for the laces is for getting around protection, multicolored one removes their one realistic use.  Which makes them even less playable than they already on.  Maybe a multicolored lace that lets you choose which colors you which of the two colors.  Prismatic Lace is really the only one that playable and just barely.</span>\n<div class=\"postDetails\" id=\"ctl00_ctl00_ctl00_MainContent_SubContent_SubContent_popularPosts_postsRepeater_ctl02_postDetails\" style=\"padding-top: 5px;\">\n<div class=\"reportAbuse\">\n<a href=\"../../Classes/Controls/#\" id=\"ctl00_ctl00_ctl00_MainContent_SubContent_SubContent_popularPosts_postsRepeater_ctl02_reportAbuseLink\" onclick=\"HandleReportPost(this, '92028'); return false;\">\r\n                                    Report Abuse</a>\u00a0\u00a0\r\n                                    \r\n                            </div>\n<div class=\"postedBy\">\r\n                                Posted By: \r\n                                <span id=\"PostedBy633\">Deathtamoor</span>\r\n                                (7/30/2010 10:53:25 PM)\r\n                            </div>\n<div class=\"postRating\">\n<div class=\"postRatingLabel\">\r\n                                    Rating:\u00a0\r\n                                </div>\n<div style=\"float: left;\">\n<div class=\"starRating\" id=\"ctl00_ctl00_ctl00_MainContent_SubContent_SubContent_popularPosts_postsRepeater_ctl02_postRating_starRating\"><img alt=\"0.5\" src=\"../../Images/Stars/LeftClearSmall.png\"/><img alt=\"1.0\" src=\"../../Images/Stars/RightClearSmall.png\"/><img alt=\"1.5\" src=\"../../Images/Stars/LeftClearSmall.png\"/><img alt=\"2.0\" src=\"../../Images/Stars/Right