      "id": "PopularPost150991",
      "post_content": "Protection from a colour works even if the source is multicolured as long as it has the colour. So prot red protects from for example U/R sources. So if we'd had a rainbow lace then using it for StP targeting a whie knight would save him.  \n  \nSo I'm for a rainbow lace.",
